{%- comment -%}
  LSC Collection Treatments
  Custom categorised treatments page replacing the default collection grid.
  Matches the approved HTML mockup with 4 treatment groups, jump links,
  treatment cards with images/prices, and a consultation CTA.
  Only renders when collection.handle == 'treatments'.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if collection.handle == 'treatments' -%}

{%- comment -%} Hide default Dawn collection-banner and main-collection sections {%- endcomment -%}
<style>
  /* Hide default Dawn collection-banner and main-collection sections */
  #shopify-section-collection-banner,
  #shopify-section-main,
  [id^="shopify-section-"][id*="collection-banner"],
  [id^="shopify-section-"][id*="__main"] {
    display: none !important;
  }
</style>

{%- comment -%}
  Build a lookup of collection products by handle for reliable image access.
  This avoids all_products limits and Liquid errors.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%} ── Page Header ── {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="lsc-ct__header">
