  <h1 class="lsc-ct__title">Clinic Treatments</h1>
  <p class="lsc-ct__intro">Advanced laser, injectable, and skin renewal treatments — all medically overseen and personalised to you.</p>
  <div class="lsc-ct__jumps">
    <a href="#laser" class="lsc-ct__jump">Laser</a>
    <a href="#injectables" class="lsc-ct__jump">Injectables</a>
    <a href="#skin" class="lsc-ct__jump">Skin Renewal</a>
    <a href="#body" class="lsc-ct__jump">Body & Face</a>
